    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚顶级葡萄酒生产商遭遇打击，廉价葡萄酒遭消费者冷遇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/australia-s-top-winemaker-reports-soft-demand-for-cheap-bottles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚最大的葡萄酒生产商警告称，全球消费者希望减少饮酒量，但提高葡萄酒价格，这挤压了 Treasury Wine Estates Ltd. 来自低成本品牌的利润，并将拖累全年盈利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/australia-s-top-winemaker-reports-soft-demand-for-cheap-bottles</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 03:53:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
